{"tid":2075326,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"博爾頓：不會投票給拜登　不支持特朗普連任, 只期望有奇蹟出現，共和黨可有一位保守派參選人。","createTime":"2020-06-22T19:15:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T19:26:09.000Z","uid":360777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8652d246818e0c9f471551ed63b4becafb6bc4","tid":2075326,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:15:51.000Z","msg":"曾為特朗普政府出任國家安全顧問的博爾頓表明，不會投票給民主黨總統參選人拜登，亦不會支持競逐連任的特朗普。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓接受《美國廣播公司》訪問時，批評特朗普經常作出飄忽不定和非理性的決定，無法將自己的個人利益和國家利益分開處理，形容特朗普擔任總統只會對國家造成危險的傷害，認為今年的總統大選是保護國家免受特朗普破壞的最後防線。<br />\n<br />\n博爾頓又說，不支持拜登和特朗普，只期望有奇蹟出現，共和黨可有一位保守派參選人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533516-20200623.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533516-20200623.htm&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7iiczFR88nQiTnqliI8U3YY%3D&h=38845025\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533516-20200623.htm&h=13f1bae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533516-20200623.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9cf37ca8d5d7256cb886b02e47d33785c2e8f1f9","tid":2075326,"uid":277702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:17:50.000Z","msg":"佢都係想彭斯出嚟選啫"},{"pid":"e82786578d859526dbac86cb1fee66eebe2546e9","tid":2075326,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cf37ca8d5d7256cb886b02e47d33785c2e8f1f9","tid":2075326,"uid":277702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:17:50.000Z","msg":"佢都係想彭斯出嚟選啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:19:19.000Z","msg":"彭斯點都唔會起trump尾注掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2258efa67c9be9853a448c6fa812a113e04baa62","tid":2075326,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-arn2-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p235x350/22489980_13708713463